comments: Iwundu (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Noah (MEM) and does not deliver contact.
RAR shows Noah (MEM) places two hands on Vucevic (ORL) in the post and the contact affects his position and ability to gather the ball.
Conley (MEM) makes marginal contact with Iwundu (ORL) off ball that does not affect his ability to defend the pass.
Wright (MEM) makes some contact with Isaac's (ORL) arm but does not affect his ability to get the rebound.
Bradley (MEM) makes some contact with Ross's (ORL) arm prior to the pick but does not affect his SQBR.
Valanciunas (MEM) cleanly blocks Iwundu's (ORL) shot attempt near the rim.
Wright (MEM) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Valanciunas (MEM) slightly extends his arm against Iwundu (ORL) during the pick but it does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Iwundu (ORL) makes contact to Wright's (MEM) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Miles (MEM) places two hands around Issac (ORL) and the contact affects his FOM.
Vucevic (ORL) slightly extends his arms against Miles (MEM) during the pick but he is able to move through the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Ross (ORL) moves his pivot foot heel-to-toe to create space.
Valanciunas (MEM) slides over and establishes himself in a legal guarding position, absorbing the contact with Ross (ORL).  He then cleanly dislodges the ball from Ross.
Ross (ORL) commits a take foul on Conley (MEM).
[Observable in enhanced video] Ross (ORL) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Iwundu (ORL) and does not deliver contact.
Isaac (ORL) releases the inbound pass within five seconds.
Holiday (MEM) makes contact with Ross's (ORL) arm but the contact is marginal and does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Bradley (MEM) makes marginal contact with Ross's (ORL) off-arm that does not cause him to lose control of the ball.
Vucevic (ORL) extends his arm towards Bradley (MEM) during the screen but the contact is marginal and Bradley is able to move through it.
RAR shows Isaac (ORL) makes contact to the arm of Conley (MEM) that affects his SQBR.
Conley (MEM) makes incidental contact to the body of Ross (ORL) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Vucevic (ORL) commits a take foul on Holiday (MEM).
